sequenceDiagram
    participant vLLM as vLLM/SGLang Pod<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ PUB
    participant ZMQ as ZMQ Subscriber<br/>5557/TCP ZMQ SUB
    participant Pool as kvevents.Pool<br/>Sharded Workers (4x)
    participant Adapter as EngineAdapter<br/>(vLLM/SGLang)
    participant Index as kvblock.Index<br/>(InMemory/Redis)
    participant EPP as Host Scheduler (EPP)
    participant Indexer as kvcache.Indexer
    participant TokenProc as TokenProcessor<br/>FNV-64a
    participant Scorer as KVBlockScorer
    participant TokenClient as UdsTokenizer Client<br/>gRPC over UDS
    participant TokenServer as UDS Tokenizer Server<br/>Python gRPC
    participant Render as vLLM OpenAIServingRender<br/>CPU mode
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over vLLM, Index: Flow 1: KV-Event Ingestion (Write Path)
    vLLM->>ZMQ: BlockStored/BlockRemoved/AllBlocksCleared<br/>ZMQ msgpack, no encryption
    ZMQ->>Pool: Dispatch to worker<br/>FNV-1a(podID) → worker shard
    Pool->>Adapter: Decode msgpack message
    Adapter->>Adapter: Extract engine key + token chunk
    Adapter->>Index: Add(engineKey, requestKey, podID)<br/>or Evict(engineKey, podID)

    Note over EPP, Scorer: Flow 2: Pod Scoring (Read Path)
    EPP->>Indexer: ScoreTokens(modelID, tokens, podIDs)
    Indexer->>TokenProc: ComputeBlockKeys(tokens, blockSize)
    TokenProc->>TokenProc: FNV-64a hash per block
    Indexer->>Index: Lookup(requestKeys)
    Index-->>Indexer: blockKey → []podIDs
    Indexer->>Scorer: Score(podCacheHits)
    Scorer-->>Indexer: map[podID]float64
    Indexer-->>EPP: Scored pod rankings

    Note over TokenClient, HF: Flow 3: Tokenization (Sidecar)
    EPP->>TokenClient: Tokenize(prompt, modelID)
    TokenClient->>TokenServer: gRPC TokenizeRequest<br/>UDS /tmp/tokenizer/tokenizer-uds.socket
    TokenServer->>Render: apply_chat_template()
    Note right of TokenServer: First call downloads<br/>tokenizer model
    TokenServer-->>HF: GET model tokenizer files<br/>HTTPS 443, HF Token (optional)
    HF-->>TokenServer: Tokenizer artifacts
    Render-->>TokenServer: Token IDs
    TokenServer-->>TokenClient: gRPC TokenizeResponse
    TokenClient-->>EPP: []int32 token IDs

    Note over vLLM, Index: Flow 4: KV-Cache Offloading (fs_backend)
    vLLM->>vLLM: OffloadingConnector.start_store()
    Note right of vLLM: llmd_fs_backend plugin<br/>GPU → Host → Storage
    vLLM->>vLLM: CUDA memcpy D2H (GPU→CPU)
    vLLM->>vLLM: POSIX write to NFS/PVC<br/>or NIXL object store
